    <item>
      <title>EF Hutton 重组后因合作伙伴解决法律纠纷而解散</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/revived-ef-hutton-breaks-up-as-partners-resolve-legal-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[EF Hutton 是一家历史悠久的华尔街公司，曾作为领先的 SPAC 投资银行而重生。然而，在重振该品牌的两家合作伙伴同意放弃对彼此的诉讼并分道扬镳之后，该公司将解散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/revived-ef-hutton-breaks-up-as-partners-resolve-legal-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 18:23:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
